Resurfacing A Previous Commission And Making air Something New! 💙💙💙
This particular set was actually for a commercial project, but we ended up going in a different direction with size and color choices so I was left with these babies unfinished for a while. They were tucked away in the studio until I decided to put them for sale! Now I’m so excited because their new forever home is with an old friend of mine from back home in Baton Rouge! 
These came out absolutely amazing and the details are even more stunning in person.
